race.comment: HOTIM ENGLISH (2) recorded another success over 1200m, making it two straight wins this campaign. Keeps improving and can win again with Todd sticking aboard. ITWASONLYAKISS (4) resumes and was last seen winning over a mile at Donald (Victoria), 147 days ago. He's certainly good enough, and the betting should guide to his readiness. HELL FIRE MISS (6) has been racing well without winning. Has the blinkers on again and briefly freshened is worth another chance. CRAZY BRAVE (1) was quickly back on track, placing close up. Maps for a soft run and has been kept on the fresh side. In the mix. SHAKATTAK (3) mixes the form but won't be far away.
